OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1783973917
OL,3,CHollywood star Kevin Bacon sends
OL,4,Cmessage to Jersey namesake
OL,6,FHollywood actor Kevin Bacon has sent a
OL,7,Fgood luck video message to a man with
OL,8,Fthe same name who is embarking on a
OL,9,F750-mile challenge to run every road
OL,10,Fin the Channel Island of Jersey for
OL,11,Fcharity.
OL,13,FThe American said he was "super proud
OL,14,Fto share my name with you" and that he
OL,15,Fwas doing something "incredible".
OL,17,FJersey's Kevin Bacon responded with
OL,18,Fshock and challenged the actor to
OL,19,Faccompany him on one of his jogs.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/3
