OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1783973917
OL,3,CHollywood star Kevin Bacon sends
OL,4,Cmessage to Jersey namesake
OL,6,F"Come and join me for a run, let's see
OL,7,Fthe island together," he said.
OL,9,FSo far, Mr Bacon has covered roughly
OL,10,Ftwo thirds of Jersey's roads and is
OL,11,Ftracking his progress on a specially
OL,12,Fdesigned tool.
OL,14,FHe told ITV News that he runs every
OL,15,Fday after work and is expecting to
OL,16,Ffinish his challenge by September.
OL,18,F"I think this island is spectacular so
OL,19,Fit's lovely to see parts of it I
OL,20,Fwouldn't normally see," Mr Bacon adds.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/3
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
