PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1783973917
OL,3,CHollywood star Kevin Bacon sends
OL,4,Cmessage to Jersey namesake
OL,6,F"I would always look at the little
OL,7,Flanes and think, I wonder where that
OL,8,Fgoes, I wonder where that pops out?
OL,10,F"I thought maybe I'll try and run it."
OL,12,FThe runner is aiming to raise #2,500
OL,13,Ffor Friends of Jersey Oncology,
OL,14,Freaching close to #1,500 so far.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/3
